---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Plano Roofing & Insurance Restoration | Free Roof Inspection"
  description="Plano roofing specialists for storm damage, insurance restoration, roof repair, and roof replacement."
>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Plano Roofing & Insurance Restoration Specialists</h1>

      <p>
        Storm damage inspections, roof repair, insurance claim assistance, and
        full roof replacement throughout Plano and surrounding areas.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Get Free Roof Inspection
        </a>

        <a href="tel:+16824859557" class="btn btn-secondary"> Call Now </a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:25px;font-size:0.95rem;">
        ✔ Free inspections &nbsp; ✔ Insurance claim support &nbsp; ✔ Local
        Plano roofing experts
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="trust-bar">
    Licensed • Insured • Storm Damage Specialists • Insurance Restoration
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Roofing Services</h2>

      <p class="section-text">
        Professional roofing and storm restoration services designed to help
        homeowners recover quickly after hail, wind, and storm damage.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Storm Damage Inspections</h3>

          <p>
            Detailed roof inspections with photo documentation for insurance
            claims.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Insurance Claim Assistance</h3>

          <p>
            Guidance through the insurance restoration process from inspection
            to approval.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Roof Repair</h3>

          <p>
            Fast repair services for leaks, missing shingles, and damaged
            roofing systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Roof Replacement</h3>

          <p>
            Full roof replacement using durable, high-quality roofing materials.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Process</h2>

      <p class="section-text">
        A straightforward roofing restoration process focused on speed,
        documentation, and quality workmanship.
      </p>

      <ol>
        <li>Schedule your free roof inspection</li>
        <li>We inspect and document storm damage</li>
        <li>Insurance claim assistance and adjuster coordination</li>
        <li>Roof repair or replacement completion</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Common Roof Problems We Find</h2>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Hidden Hail Damage</h3>

          <p>
            Storm damage often invisible from the ground after severe weather.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Wind Damage</h3>

          <p>Missing shingles and lifted roofing materials caused by storms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Roof Leaks</h3>

          <p>Interior water damage caused by compromised roofing systems.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Insurance Underpayment</h3>

          <p>Claims that fail to account for the full scope of storm damage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta">
        <h2>Is Your Roof Storm-Damaged?</h2>

        <p>
          Small roofing issues can become expensive repairs if ignored. Schedule
          a free inspection today.
        </p>

        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary"> Request Free Inspection </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
